mir Adnan Menderes Airport|Izmir]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Qatar Airways]]| [[Hamad International Airport|Doha]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Qeshm Air]]| [[Tehran Imam Khomeini International Airport|Tehran\u2013Imam Khomeini]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Red Wings Airlines]]| [[Kazan International Airport|Kazan]], [[Moscow Domodedovo Airport|Moscow\u2013Domodedovo]], [[Platov International Airport|Rostov-on-Don]], [[Pulkovo Airport|Saint Petersburg]], [[Ufa International Airport|Ufa]], [[Koltsovo International Airport|Yekaterinburg]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Rossiya Airlines]]| [[Pulkovo Airport|Saint Petersburg]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Royal Air Maroc]]| [[Mohammed V International Airport|Casablanca]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Royal Jordanian]]| [[Queen Alia International Airport|Amman\u2013Queen Alia]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Saudia]]| [[King Abdulaziz International Airport|Jeddah]], [[Prince Mohammad bin Abdulaziz International Airport|Medina]], [[King Khalid International Airport|Riyadh]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[SCAT Airlines]]| [[Aktau Airport|Aktau]], [[Shymkent International Airport|Shymkent]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Sichuan Airlines]]| [[Chengdu Shuangliu International Airport|Chengdu]] \n<!-- -->\n|[[Singapore Airlines]]| [[Singapore Changi Airport|Singapore]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Somon Air]]| [[Dushanbe International Airport|Dushanbe]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Taban Air]]| [[Isfahan International Airport|Isfahan]], [[Tehran Imam Khomeini International Airport|Tehran\u2013Imam Khomeini]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[TAROM]]| [[Henri Coand\u0103 International Airport|Bucharest]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Transavia France]]| [[Nantes Atlantique Airport|Nantes]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Tunisair]]| [[Tunis\u2013Carthage International Airport|Tunis]]\n<!-- -->\n|[[Turkish Airlines]]| [[F\u00e9lix-Houphou\u00ebt-Boigny International Airport|Abidjan]], [[Abu Dhabi International Airport|Abu Dhabi]], [[Nnamdi Azikiwe International Airport|Abuja]], [[Kotoka International Airport|Accra]], [[Adana \u015eakirpa\u015fa Airport|Adana]], [[Addis Ababa Bole International Airport|Addis Ababa]], [[Ad\u0131yaman Airport|Ad\u0131