e=Defender Dinu S\u00e2nm\u0103rtean left Gloria Bistrita|accessdate= 8 October 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cancan.ro/sanmartean-din-liga-1-in-liga-a-saptea-cand-nu-este-pe-teren-petrece-8-ore-pe-zi-intr-o-fabrica.html|title=Sanmartean din Liga 1 in liga a saptea! Cand nu este pe teren, petrece 8 ore pe zi intr-o fabrica!|publisher=cancan.ro|language=Romanian |trans-title=Sanmartean from the Liga 1 to the seventh league! When not in the field, he spends 8 hours a day in a factory!|accessdate= 8 October 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Career statistics==\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n! rowspan=2 | Club\n! rowspan=2 | Season\n! colspan=3 | League\n! colspan=2 | Cup\n! colspan=2 | League Cup\n! colspan=2 | Continental\n! colspan=2 | Other\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n! Division\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n|-\n|rowspan=7|[[ACF Gloria 1922 Bistri\u0163a|Gloria Bistri\u0163a]]||[[1998\u201399 Divizia A|1998\u201399]]||rowspan=6|[[Liga I|Divizia A]]||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||1||0\n|-\n|[[1999\u20132000 Divizia A|1999\u201300]]||9||0||2||0||2||1||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||13||1\n|-\n|[[2000\u201301 Divizia A|2000\u201301]]||26||2||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=2|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||28||2\n|-\n|[[2001\u201302 Divizia A|2001\u201302]]||27||3||2||1||colspan=2|\u2013||1||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||30||4\n|-\n|[[2002\u201303 Divizia A|2002\u201303]]||26||7||1||0||colspan=2|\u2013||3||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||30||7\n|-\n|[[2003\u201304 Divizia A|2003\u201304]]||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||3||3||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||3||3\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total\n!89||12||7||1||2||1||7||3||0||0||105||17\n|-\n|rowspan=3|[[Panathinaikos F.C.|Panathinaikos]]||[[Alpha Ethniki 2003\u201304|2003\u201304]]||rowspan=2|[[Superleague Greece|Alpha Ethniki]]||18||1||4||1||rows